#: frontend/templates/portal_publik/index.html:123
msgid ""
"Wujudkan tata kelola pemerintahan yang akuntabel melalui keterbukaan data "
"aset daerah Kota Palu. Akses informasi tanah, bangunan, dan aset lainnya "
"secara real-time."
msgstr ""
"Realize accountable public governance through the transparency of Palu "
"City's regional asset data. Access information on land, buildings, and other "
"assets in real-time."

