#: frontend/templates/portal_publik/index.html:213
msgid "Bidang Aset BPKAD Kota Palu"
msgstr "Asset Division of BPKAD Palu City"

#: frontend/templates/portal_publik/index.html:215
msgid ""
"Badan Pengelola Keuangan dan Aset Daerah (BPKAD) Kota Palu melalui Bidang "
"Aset berkomitmen untuk mengelola kekayaan daerah secara profesional, "
"transparan, dan akuntabel. Kami memastikan setiap aset daerah tercatat "
"dengan baik dan dimanfaatkan secara optimal untuk kepentingan masyarakat."
msgstr ""
"The Regional Financial and Asset Management Agency (BPKAD) of Palu City, "
"through the Asset Division, is committed to managing regional wealth "
"professionally, transparently, and accountably. We ensure every regional "
"asset is well-recorded and optimally utilized for the benefit of the "
"community."

#: frontend/templates/portal_publik/index.html:218
msgid ""
"Sistem Pataba hadir sebagai jembatan informasi antara pemerintah dan "
"masyarakat dalam memantau sebaran dan status hukum aset-aset strategis di "
"wilayah Kota Palu."
msgstr ""
"The Pataba System serves as an information bridge between the government and "
"the community in monitoring the distribution and legal status of strategic "
"assets in the Palu City area."

#: frontend/templates/portal_publik/index.html:221
