#: frontend/templates/portal_publik/index.html:237
msgid ""
"Jelajahi berbagai kategori aset daerah yang dikelola oleh Pemerintah Kota "
"Palu melalui basis data terintegrasi."
msgstr ""
"Explore various categories of regional assets managed by the Palu City "
"Government through an integrated database."

